relation: Darrow1 - #30 What will happen to our heroes?! Will they be trapped for eternity...? Actually, no. With the story switching to our new temporary hero, there is only one thing left to fear: Tony.

Darrow1 - #31 Jeff begins his attempt to steal the spotlight with Tony following close behind. While Jeff is challenging Ness on the front of heroic poses, Paula will have to be wary of the fact that Tony is sporting a killer hairstyle.
Darrow1 - #32 Jeff and Tony check around and steal some cookies while obtaining information on Maxwell. Fortunately, Maxwell doesn't actually watch the kids and could care less what happens to them!
Darrow1 - #33 Maxwell provides his assistance in the form of a...key? Well, it was a key at one point. Also, a disturbing look into the supposed life of Dr. Andonuts.
Darrow1 - #34 Jeff and Tony bid farewell to Maxwell as they head into the locker room for Jeff to arm up. Tony, of course, is all too excited about the results.
